list.name: Default
list.comment: Added working menu window with help window, best scores window and exit button. Of course there is also play button

task.summary: Added HUD and basic enemy. Implemented the borders of screen.
Added HUD and basic enemy. Implemented the borders of screen.
Added new opponent. Improved steering controls. Added points system, level system and coins system, which will have purpose in the future. Added procedurally generated enemies (through time).

Added new opponent called BallChaser that will chase white player. Finally optimized control systems so now while pressing opposite buttons, our character stays in place instead of going somewhere.
Up next: >Mini boss level >Collectibles like coins or so, which will boost score and give coins that will be used to purchase skins/upgrades in store
